headline: A Look At Tyler Technologies (TYL) Valuation After New County Payments Deal And Analyst Optimism
summary: Tyler Technologies (TYL) just signed on as the sole payment processing partner for Chesterfield County, Virginia, consolidating online and in person payments for nearly 400,000 residents through its AWS powered Tyler Payments platform. See our latest analysis for Tyler Technologies.
